{"name": "aioxmlrpc", "metadata": {"name": "aioxmlrpc", "version": "0.9.1", "classifiers": ["Development Status :: 5 - Production/Stable", "Framework :: AsyncIO", "Intended Audience :: Developers", "Intended Audience :: Information Technology", "License :: OSI Approved :: MIT License", "Topic :: Internet :: WWW/HTTP", "Topic :: Software Development :: Libraries", "Topic :: System :: Networking", "Typing :: Typed"], "home_page": null, "license": "MIT License", "documentation_url": "https://mardiros.github.io/aioxmlrpc", "dependencies": ["httpx"], "summary": "XML-RPC client for asyncio", "upload_time": 1733480035}, "documentation": ["# aioxmlrpc\n\n```{image} https://github.com/mardiros/aioxmlrpc/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg\n:target: https://github.com/mardiros/aioxmlrpc/actions/workflows/tests.yml\n```\n\n```{image} https://codecov.io/gh/mardiros/aioxmlrpc/branch/master/graph/badge.svg?token=BR3KttC9uJ\n:target: https://codecov.io/gh/mardiros/aioxmlrpc\n```\n\nAsyncio version of the standard lib `xmlrpc`\n\nCurrently only `aioxmlrpc.client`, which works like `xmlrpc.client` but\nwith coroutine is implemented.\n\nFill free to fork me if you want to implement the server part.\n\n`aioxmlrpc` is based on `httpx` for the transport, and just patch\nthe necessary from the python standard library to get it working.\n\n## Installation\n\naioxmlrpc is available on PyPI, it can simply be installed with your favorite\ntool, example with pip here.\n\n```\npip install aioxmlrpc\n```\n\n## Getting Started\n\nThis example show how to print the current version of the Gandi XML-RPC api.\n\n```\nimport asyncio\nfrom aioxmlrpc.client import ServerProxy\n\n\n@asyncio.coroutine\ndef print_gandi_api_version():\n    api = ServerProxy('https://rpc.gandi.net/xmlrpc/')\n    result = yield from api.version.info()\n    print(result)\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n    loop = asyncio.get_event_loop()\n    loop.run_until_complete(print_gandi_api_version())\n    loop.stop()\n```\n\nRun the example\n\n```\nuv run examples/gandi_api_version.py\n```\n"], "modules": [{"name": "aioxmlrpc", "documentation": ["XML-RPC Protocol for ``asyncio``"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "aioxmlrpc.__version__", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [], "exports": [{"name": "aioxmlrpc.metadata", "xref": {"fqname": "importlib.metadata", "project": null}}]}, {"name": "aioxmlrpc.client", "documentation": ["XML-RPC Client with asyncio.\n\nThis module adapt the `xmlrpc.client` module of the standard library to\nwork with asyncio.\n"], "functions": [], "variables": [{"name": "aioxmlrpc.client.__ALL__", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "aioxmlrpc.client.RPCResult", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "aioxmlrpc.client.RPCParameters", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "aioxmlrpc.client.Fault", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "aioxmlrpc.client.ProtocolError", "type": null, "documentation": []}, {"name": "aioxmlrpc.client.log", "type": null, "documentation": []}], "classes": [{"name": "aioxmlrpc.client._Method", "bases": [], "methods": [{"name": "aioxmlrpc.client._Method.__init__", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "send", "type": {"name": "Callable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Callable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "", "xref": null, "params": [{"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "RPCParameters", "xref": {"fqname": "RPCParameters", "project": null}, "params": null}]}, {"name": "Awaitable", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Awaitable", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "RPCResult", "xref": {"fqname": "RPCResult", "project": null}, "params": null}]}]}, "default": null}, {"name": "name", "type": {"name": "str", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.str", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "None", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "-